title_page: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Evening' game
maintext:
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday evening’s drawing of the Ohio Lottery’s “Pick 4 Evening” game were:
4-7-6-1
(four, seven, six, one)
